Package org.janusproject.acl

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ACLMessageContent
    This interface describes the Content of a given ACL Message as defined by FIPA.
    ACLMessageEnvelope
    This interface describes the Envelope of a given ACL Message as defined by FIPA.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ACLAgent
    Implements the agent concept of the Janus Metamodel with the ability to manage ACL Messages.
    ACLMessage
    This class precises the minimal set of attributes required by an ACL Message to be sent and received.
    ACLMessage.Content
    This inner-class represents the content of the ACL Message.
    ACLMessage.Envelope
    This inner-class represents the envelope of the ACL Message.
    ACLMessageHandler
    This class handles the transmission of the ACLMessage before/after encoding and decoding
    ACLTransportMessage
    This class extends ObjectMessage and is used to transport the encoded ACLMessage (payload) via the Message Transport Service
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ACLRepresentation
    This enumeration describes all available ACL Representations as defined by Fipa.
    Performative
    This enumeration describes all available performatives as defined by FIPA
